overview:
AllTranscript.com is a online transcription service company for all types of general,legal audio and video transcriptions.

Transcription is done by professional typists with a high level of accuracy. Prices for transcription starts at US$ 1.10 per minute with a 3 day turnaround. There are no extra charges for difficult audio,multiple speakers or timestamps.

Clientele of Alltranscript.com includes some big universities such as MIT,UCLA and other independent niches including journalists,lawyers,investigators,broadcasters,radio shows and public coaches.
